import numpy as np
import cv2 as cv
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
In [ ]:
img =cv.imread("D:\Academics\Semester 4\Machine Vision\Homeworks\Documents\Homework2\spider.png")
assert img is not None

gamma_values = [0.2,0.8,1.2,2]
for gamma in gamma_values:
    t = np.array([(p/255)**gamma*255 for p in range (0,256)]).astype(np.uint8)
    gImg = cv.LUT(img,t)

    cv.namedWindow('Image',cv.WINDOW_AUTOSIZE)
    cv.imshow('Image',img)
    cv.waitKey(0)
    cv.imshow('Image',gImg)
    cv.waitKey(0)
    cv.destroyAllWindows()


    plt.figure(figsize=(16, 8))
    plt.subplot(1,2,1)
    implot = plt.imshow(cv.cvtColor(gImg, cv.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
    plt.imshow(cv.cvtColor(gImg,cv.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
    plt.axis('off')

    plt.subplot(1,2,2)
    plt.plot(t)

    plt.suptitle( "Gamma = {}".format(gamma), fontsize=12)

    plt.show()

t1 = np.linspace(0,100,50)
t2 = np.linspace(100,255,150)
t3 = np.linspace(255,255,56)

t = np.concatenate((t1,t2,t3),axis = 0).astype(np.uint8)
g = cv.LUT(img,t)


cv.namedWindow('Image',cv.WINDOW_AUTOSIZE)
cv.imshow('Image',img)
cv.waitKey(0)
cv.imshow('Image',g)
cv.waitKey(0)
cv.destroyAllWindows()

f = cv.imread("D:\Academics\Semester 4\Machine Vision\Homeworks\Documents\Homework2\zion_pass.jpg")
assert f is not None

hsv  = cv.cvtColor(f, cv.COLOR_BGR2HSV)

for x in range(0, len(hsv)):
    for y in range(0, len(hsv[0])):
        hsv[x, y][1] += 50

img = cv.cvtColor(hsv, cv.COLOR_HSV2BGR)

cv.namedWindow('Image', cv.WINDOW_AUTOSIZE)
cv.imshow('Image', f)
cv.waitKey(0)
cv.imshow('Image', img)
cv.waitKey(0)

cv.destroyAllWindows()

plt.figure(figsize = (16,12))
plt.subplot(1,2,1)
implot = plt.imshow(cv.cvtColor(f,cv.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
plt.axis('off')

plt.subplot(1,2,2)
implot = plt.imshow(cv.cvtColor(img, cv.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
plt.axis('off')

plt.show()
